high_descs: Turn around, go forward and to the left to the sink.
Take the large knife from the sink's drying rack.
Cut the potato on the rack into slices.
Turn right, go towards the wall, turn right, go forward to the white table.
Put the knife to the right of the salt on the table.
Turn right, go forward, turn right at the sink, go to the sink.
Take a slice of potato from the sink's drying rack.
Turn right, go towards the wall, turn left to face the fridge.
Put the potato on the clear plate at the bottom of the fridge.
Take the plate from the fridge.
Turn around, go forward to the white table.
Put the plate to the left of the closest lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a slice of potato on it on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink in front of the window.
Pick up the yellow knife on the sink.
Cut up the potato on the sink.
Turn around and walk to the table in the corner with lettuce on it.
Place the knife on top of the other knife on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink in front of the window.
Pick up a piece of potato from the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the piece of potato on the clear, glass plate in the fridge.
Pick up the clear, glass plate from the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the table with lettuce on it.
Place the plate behind the paper towels on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled, clear, glass plate with a piece of potato on it onto the table in the corner.

high_descs: Turn around, turn left, and walk across the room to the sink.
Pick up the knife.
Slice the potato on the sink.
Turn right, walk across the room, turn right, and walk to the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Turn right, walk across the room to the stove, turn right, and walk to the sink.
Pick up a potato slice.
Turn right, walk across the room to the fridge, and turn left.
Open the fridge, and put the potato slice in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl, and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Put the bowl on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a potato slice in a cold bowl, and put the bowl on the table.
